    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "``` js\nclass MyTemplateComponent extends React.Component {\n    render(){\n        return <div>{JSON.stringify(this.props,null,2)}</div>;\n    }\n}\n\nsearch.addWidget(\n    instantsearch.widgets.hits({\n        templates : { hit: MyTemplateComponent }\n    })\n);\n```\n\nSomething like that?\n",
